tatic.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131182763,imgsize-147244.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[UK weather forecast: 26°C scorcher on the way, hotter than Athens and Barcelona]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131182277.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Britain is set for a dramatic temperature rise towards the end of the week, with highs of 26°C predicted for Friday in the south east. Following a cold snap in early May, forecasters now anticipate settled sunshine and warmer weather for England and Wales throughout the bank holiday weekend, offering a welcome change from recent unsettled conditions.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-weather-forecast-26c-scorcher-on-the-way-hotter-than-athens-and-barcelona/articleshow/131182277.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-weather-forecast-26c-scorcher-on-the-way-hotter-than-athens-and-barcelona/articleshow/131182277.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-18T22:35:40+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131182280,imgsize-196938.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Texas man films Indian grocery store keeping food items out in the open, owner says he's a Trump voter]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131181486.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/texas-man-films-indian-grocery-store-keeping-food-items-out-in-the-open-owner-says-hes-a-trump-voter/articleshow/131181486.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/texas-man-films-indian-grocery-store-keeping-food-items-out-in-the-open-owner-says-hes-a-trump-voter/articleshow/131181486.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-18T22:07:42+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131181622,imgsize-61400.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[In God We Trump: MAGA's Project Big MAC (Make America Christian) unfolds on the Mall]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131181400.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A recent prayer event in Washington, backed by the White House, has sparked debate about religion and nationalism. Thousands gathered for 'Rededicate 250,' with speakers advocating for America to be a Christian nation. This event highlights a trend of merging American identity with Christianity, a move critics liken to a 'Make America Christian' project.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/in-god-we-trump-magas-project-big-mac-make-america-christian-unfolds-on-the-mall/articleshow/131181400.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/in-god-we-trump-magas-project-big-mac-make-america-christian-unfolds-on-the-mall/articleshow/131181400.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-18T21:55:03+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Chidanand Rajghatta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131181388,imgsize-1049154.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Taiwan &amp; Thucydides Trap: How close have the US and China come to conflict before?]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131177148.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Taiwan, a flashpoint in US-China rivalry, is increasingly central to global tensions. President Xi Jinping's "Thucydides Trap" warning highlights the risk of conflict as China rises.  The island'