+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131171195,imgsize-1051924.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Trump’s cryptic Gulf map with red arrows at Iran sparks fresh war fears]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131170248.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[US President Trump has ignited controversy by tweeting a provocative map aimed at Iran, declaring that 'the clock is ticking' in reference to potential military engagement. This revelation comes on the heels of his discussions with Israeli PM Netanyahu, signaling escalating tensions.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/trumps-cryptic-gulf-map-with-red-arrows-at-iran-sparks-fresh-war-fears/articleshow/131170248.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/trumps-cryptic-gulf-map-with-red-arrows-at-iran-sparks-fresh-war-fears/articleshow/131170248.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-18T13:34:53+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131170623,imgsize-1087528.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[US, Nigeria launch fresh kinetic strikes on ISIS targets]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131170707.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[US Africa Command, in coordination with Nigeria, conducted kinetic strikes against ISIS militants in Northeastern Nigeria. This operation follows the recent killing of a top ISIS leader, Abu-Bilal al-Minuki, in a joint US-Nigerian mission. The strikes aim to diminish ISIS's capacity to plan attacks threatening regional and US security.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/us-nigeria-launch-fresh-kinetic-strikes-on-isis-targets/articleshow/131170707.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/us-nigeria-launch-fresh-kinetic-strikes-on-isis-targets/articleshow/131170707.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-18T13:39:06+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131170746,imgsize-25200.cms"/></item></channel></rss>